Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:34.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,原创字幕: 人人影视\NYYeTs.com\N时间轴：wsr
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:35.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不可能这么简单\NIt cannot be that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:37.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你看见这些灯亮了\NYou saw these lights come on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:40.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,对  太阳能板放在月亮下\NYeah, when these solar panels were exposed to the moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.44,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,或许就变成了月亮能板\NWhich I guess makes them lunar panels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.43,0:00:45.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,还记不记得在集中营里\NHey, you remember in the camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:47.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们发现激光围墙\Nwhen we figured out that the laser wall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.45,0:00:48.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是靠飞艇供能的\Nwas powered by the dirigible?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:50.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,对  我觉得这里可能也是同一原理\NRight. I think the same principle is at play here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:52.34,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,只不过尺度大很多\Nexcept on a much bigger scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:55.32,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我觉得艾士芬尼全部科技所需的能量\NI think the Espheni are powering all their tech
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:56.80,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,都来自同一能量源\Noff the same power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:59.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-月光  -不\N- Moonlight? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:02.44,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是从月亮发出的一种能量波\NA form of energy beamed from the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:03.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,无线电能\NWireless electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:05.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,特斯拉曾认为这是不可能的\NTesla thought it was possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:08.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,艾士芬尼一定是设法完善了\NThe Espheni must have finally perfected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:11.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这也意味着艾士芬尼的能量核\NAnd it suggests that the Espheni power core,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:14.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们的侦察小组费了无数心思\Nwhich our Volm recon teams have found so difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:15.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,想在地球上找到的能量核\Nto locate here on earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:18.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,从来就不在地球上\Nwas never on earth in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:23.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一直就在  我们头顶上\NIt was just... over our heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:32.71,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,科奇斯  别对自己这么苛刻\NHey, Cochise, don't beat yourself up so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我需要单独待一会儿\NI need to be alone for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:42.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你觉得他们为什么把能量源建在月亮上\NSo, why do you think they built the power source on the moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:45.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,从星球轨道上获取能量的唯一原因\NThe only reason you would beam power from orbit is if --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:48.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就是希望能为地球各处提供能量\NYou wanted to have a vantage point to power the entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:50.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这么说  月亮上的能量源\NSo, the power core on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:53.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,为所有集中营的所有激光围墙供能\Nsupports every laser wall on every ghetto?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:54.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,全世界的\NAll over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:56.59,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,所有的一切  所有迅猎兽工厂\NEverything else -- every skitter factory,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们还没想象到的所有噩梦\Nevery nightmare that we haven't even imagined yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:04.71,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,能量源为整个艾士芬尼战争机器供能\NIt powers the entire Espheni war machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:07.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这么说我们的选择不多了\NWell, then I don't see that we have many options.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:09.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们得想个办法上去\NWe're gonna have to figure out a way to get up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,把那个东西炸掉\Nblow that son of a bitch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是在月亮上\NIt's on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:21.03,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-你听到了  对吧  -听到了\N- You heard that part, right? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:23.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道你在想什么  丹\NAnd I know that look you're giving me, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:25.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我也知道你在笑什么\NAnd I know that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:28.39,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你劝疯子别跳楼的时候\NI've seen it when you've tried to talk some crazy bastard
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:29.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就是这个表情\Nfrom jumping off of a ledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:31.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那我告诉你  今天我就是那个疯子\NWell, guess what. Today the crazy bastard is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:38.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好吧  咱们研究研究\NAll right. Let's, uh -- let's talk this thing through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:41.62,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,首先  怎么到那里\NFirstly, how do we gain access to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:43.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-不知道  -好吧\N- I don't know. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:46.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我确定  就算咱们真找到办法\NAnd I'm pretty sure that if we do unearth it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:47.78,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-情况也不乐观  -不知道\N- it's gonna be a little beat-up. - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:50.07,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果我们真找到了开关  或许能\NAnd, hey, if we find that "on" switch, maybe we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:51.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不知道  不知道  不知道\NI don't know. I don't know. I don't know. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:53.52,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,别说了\NStop saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:54.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们选择去月球\NWe choose to go to the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不是因为简单  而是因为困难\Nnot because it's easy but because it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:59.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好吧  还开上玩笑了  你觉得好玩吗\NOkay, so, this is funny? This is funny to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:00.43,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,等等  等我说完\NHang on. Let me finish the speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:01.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,因为不管你们信不信\NBecause, believe it or not, the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:04.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我第一次听到的时候  我原来也没想到\Nthat I heard that speech, I was crazy enough to think
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:06.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,肯尼迪是在跟我说话\Nthat JFK was actually talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:09.52,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,因为这就是我们要接受的挑战\N'Cause that is a challenge that we are willing to accept --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:12.47,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们不愿再推迟\None that we are unwilling to postpone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:13.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们必须胜利\Nand one which we intend to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:18.07,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,汤姆  我们没法飞到月亮上去\NOkay, Tom, we cannot fly to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:22.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们不一定要飞上去\NW-well, we wouldn't necessarily have to fly to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.15,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,科奇斯\NCochise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:29.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,跟我假设一下\NJust play it a little hypothetical with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:31.92,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果能量源在月亮上\NIf the power core is on the moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.30,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那里是不是应该有艾士芬尼的某种基地\Nwouldn't it follow the Espheni have some kind of base up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:36.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,应该是的\NIn all likelihood, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:40.15,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,既然我们知道激光飞船是遥控的\NOkay, well, since we know that beamers are controlled remotely,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:42.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果我们能找到一个方法\Nif we can figure out a way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:45.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,把月球基地设置为目的地\Nto set the moon base as a destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:48.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,咱们不就只需要搭个便车吗\Nwouldn't all we need to do is hitch a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:50.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我都不相信我会这么说\NI cannot believe I am saying this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你这话并没有听上去那么疯狂\Nbut it is not as crazy as it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这话比听上去疯多了\NYou're right. It's crazier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.76,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,只有这一个办法\NI honestly don't see any other alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:00.44,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,仔细想想\NI mean, think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:03.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,摧毁了一个迅猎兽工厂\NYou...close down a skitter factory,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:04.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,解放了一个集中营\Nliberate a camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,然后呢  我们再去下一个目标\NWhat then -- we move on to the next one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一次次地浴血奋战拯救世界吗\Nand we save the world one bloodbath at a time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不这么认为\NI don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:13.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一次性把它们彻底击败  摧毁能量源\NWe got to shut them all down at the same time, at the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:14.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,只有这个办法\NThat's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:19.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们的确有个激光飞船\NWell... we do have a beamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:22.39,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,被埋的飞船\NA buried beamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.43,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那就把它挖出来\NSo, let's unbury it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:35.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,陨落星辰\N第四季 第九集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:38.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,差不多了吧\NThink you're about full.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:41.47,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,整天工作  却完全没有进展\NAh, nothing like working all day and barely making a dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:42.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,艾士芬尼炸毁了整个城\NThe Espheni blew up the whole town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:43.87,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,得花点时间清理\NIt's gonna take some time to clean it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,感觉如何\NHow you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就像刚和迈克·泰森打了十个回合\NLike I just went 10 rounds with Mike Tyson
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.92,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他还用了指节铜环  刀子\Nand he was using brass knuckles and knives
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.55,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,还有一台压路机\Nand a steamroller.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.60,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,至少他没把你耳朵咬下来\NAt least he didn't bite your ear off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.18,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你起来干什么  应该好好休息\NWhat are you doing up? You ought to be resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:02.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你刚进行了一次外星人刺钉移植\NYou just had an alien-spike transplant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:04.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,对  现在我有外星人DNA\NYeah, and now I've got alien DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.60,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,在我的血管和肌肉里驰骋\Ncoursing through my veins and my muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:07.89,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,疼啊\NIt hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,无法集中精力  坐不住\NI can't concentrate. I can't sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:12.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我得做点什么\NI got to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,想搬一些瓦砾吗\NWant to move some rubble?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:18.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,想  最想干的就是这个了\NYeah, more than anything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:22.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你就像机器一样\NYou're like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:27.52,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我只是想说\NHey, I just want to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:28.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道你在这件事情上的态度\NI know how you feel about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:29.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我要谢谢你的支持\NAnd I want to thank you for your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不是在支持你\NI'm not supporting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.77,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我还是觉得你疯了\NI'm still thinking you're nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:39.27,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但如果大家都听从你最新的疯点子\NBut as long as you've got everyone buying into your latest brand of crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不会扫大家的兴\NI'm not gonna rain on their parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:43.39,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,上帝知道  他们没有别的希望了\NLord knows, they don't have anything else to hope for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.88,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,所以  在他们恢复理智之前\NSo, until they come to their senses,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:47.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我会支持他们\NI'm supporting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你确定就是这样吗\NYou sure that that's what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:51.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不懂你在说什么\NI don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:53.89,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,安  我是说亚蕾克西\NCome on, Anne, I'm talking about Lexi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.03,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,听我说  发生了很多事\NListen, a lot's happened --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:58.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们不应该相互埋怨\Nstuff that we shouldn't blame each other about,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:00.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们也不应该封闭自己\Nstuff that we shouldn't be keeping to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:01.60,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不同意\NI disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:03.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我觉得有些东西就是应该\NI think there are some things that are uniquely suited
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:05.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好好封闭起来\Nto keeping to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这个飞船不会自己钻出来\NThis beamer's not gonna dig itself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.15,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这里需要帮忙\NSure could use some more help out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:10.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,丁甘去哪儿了\NWhere's Dingaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.72,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他和沙一起  在下面\NHe's down there with Shaq,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,研究飞船的操控系统\Ntrying to assess the beamer controls,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,很困难  因为他们需要的那部分\Nwhich is difficult because the parts they need
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:16.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,还被埋着\Nare still buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:20.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他们不应该钻进那个烤箱一样的飞船里\NWell, they should get their asses out of that toasty-warm beamer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:22.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,应该来帮我们挖掘\Nand get to work helping us unbury it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:24.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那个被烧焦的领主不会走远的\NThat scorched overlord isn't gonna be gone long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:26.66,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,早晚会发现我们还活着\NSooner or later, he's gonna figure out some of us survived,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:28.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,到时它肯定会回来\Nand he's gonna be right back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们会夜以继日地挖掘  我保证\NWe're gonna dig around the clock. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,即使这样  也需要几周时间\NEven if we do, it's gonna take us weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.80,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我可能有个办法\NI have a possible solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:39.47,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,几英里之外  有一个隐蔽的\NThere is... A concealed Volm supply cache
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:41.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,沃尔姆补给站\Nseveral miles from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你在说什么  沃尔姆补给站\NWhat are you talking about, Volm supply cache?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.69,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们仔细研究了你们的先辈以及美国本土战争\NWe studied your pioneer and native American wars closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:50.80,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,隐秘的供给站\NHidden supply stockpiles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,对双方来说都是重要的资源\Nproved to be a vital resource for both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:57.80,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这个补给站  应该存有高科技工具\NThis cache should contain tools with advanced technology
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,可用于更快速的\Nthat could be used to break up this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:02.03,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,挖掘和清理\Nand clear it away more quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,什么  沃尔姆挖掘机吗\NWhat? Like a Volm backhoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.03,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,震荡炮\NConcussion ordnances
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:07.92,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,可以向土壤深处发射声波\Ncapable of shooting sound waves deep into the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:09.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,把石头震成沙粒\Nturning boulders into sand,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.39,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,应该能大大加速这一工程\Nwhich should expedite this process immeasurably.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,为什么现在才告诉我们\NWhy are we just hearing about this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:17.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,在最近一次攻击之前  艾士芬尼的队伍\NEspheni forces stood between this camp and the supply cache
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:19.51,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,位于补给站和这里之间\Nuntil their recent attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:22.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,现在它们减少了这一区域的侦查力量\NThey have now scaled back their reconnaissance in this area,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:25.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,危险大大降低\Nbut the risk is minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:27.54,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-卡住了吗  -我能处理\N- Is it stuck? - Oh, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-这里  -等我一下\N- Here. - Give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:36.26,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-我帮你吧  -好\N- No, let me help. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:38.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,钢筋卡住了\NIt's stuck on the rebar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:41.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-准备好了吗  -好了\N- All right, you ready? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:45.68,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,数到三  一  二  三\NOn 3. 1...2...3.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谁干的  他妈的...\NWho did that?! Motherf...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:55.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\NAre you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不好  我摔到手腕了\NNo! I fell on my wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:01.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你没事的  好吧\NAll right, look, you're -- you're fine, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.54,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的同情啊\NThanks for the sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:04.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,真抱歉\NI'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:06.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她还好吗\NHey, is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.88,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她很不好  到底他妈的怎么回事\NNo, she's not okay! What the hell was all that about, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:11.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,咱们去看看她有事没事\NLet's go make sure she's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不用了  不用了\NNo, no, no, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:14.43,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,让你这位长着迅猎兽脖子的女朋友离大家远点\NKeep your Skitter-neck girlfriend away from everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:16.51,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,艾士芬尼想杀我们  情况已经够糟糕了\NIt's bad enough we got Espheni trying to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,别管他\NDon't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:24.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他说得对  我就是一团糟\NHe's right. I'm a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我身上好痛  没法认真思考\NEverything hurts. I can't think straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:28.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.60,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不  我感觉就像在操作新机器\NNo, I feel like I'm operating new machinery,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.30,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,却没人给我说明书\Nnobody gave me the instruction manual,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:36.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我该离大家远点\Nand I should just stay away from everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:39.55,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不  我以前经历过这种事\NNo, I -- I've been through this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.55,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我可以帮助你  习惯你的感官\NI can help you -- get used to your senses,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,学习如何控制力量\Nlearn how to control your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:46.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是啊  如果你能那样做  那就太好了\NYeah, if you could do that, that would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:47.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也许你应该接受他的提议\NMaybe you ought to take him up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,去吧\NYeah, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:03.30,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,安\NAnne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:06.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你在干什么\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:09.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,韦弗跟我说了沃尔姆补给站的事\NWeaver told me about the Volm supply cache,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我想换个地方\Nand I could use some change of scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.46,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你是真的生我气了吧\NWow, you really blame me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:19.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你觉得是我让亚蕾克西改变阵营\NYou think I persuaded Lexi to switch sides
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:20.51,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,残忍地杀害了卢尔德吗\Nand murder Lourdes in cold blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:21.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你觉得那是我的主意吗\NYou think that was my idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:26.29,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但我觉得你十分愿意尝试一切\NBut I think you're more than willing to try anything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不管是多么疯狂冒险的办法\Nno matter how crazy, no matter how reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,知道吗\NAnd you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:31.60,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不想搅合进去\NI do not want to get into this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:33.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,知道吗  也许你就是该怪我\NYou know what? Maybe you should blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:35.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,因为当本告诉我们亚蕾克西的事\NBecause when Ben came and told us about Lexi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:36.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,说没有线索可以跟踪时\Nand said that there was no trail to follow,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:38.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也许我只是在寻找一个释怀的原因\Nmaybe I was looking for a reason to move on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:41.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,免得我们家的闹剧  对大家的一切\Nso that our family drama didn't wreak havoc on everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:42.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,造成严重破坏\Nand everything for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.43,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但我不能跟你说\NBut I can't discuss that with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你觉得那是新鲜事吗  汤姆\NYou think that's something new, Tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:47.89,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你一旦得出结论\NYou reach a conclusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就默认全世界都自动同意了\Nand it's like the rest of the world is automatically on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:52.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你说得没错  我觉得并非每个问题\NGuilty as charged -- I don't think that every problem
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,都需要民主的解决方案\Nhas to have a democratic solution,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但现在发生的事是你很生气\Nbut what's happening right now is that you're upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:56.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,却不愿意跟我谈论这事\NAnd instead of talking to me about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:58.51,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而是要封闭自己  逃避一切\Nyou're gonna bottle that up and live in denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我没有逃避  汤姆\NI am not living in denial, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这就是我\NThis -- this is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.80,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这就是到处奔走  努力活下来的我\NThis is me that's been on the road, surviving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:07.47,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我花了几个月时间寻找我们女儿\NThis is the me who spent months searching for our daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:08.74,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但却没有线索\Nand I didn't have a trail to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:09.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这是两码事\NThat was a little different!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你不知道她变了样\NYou didn't know what she had become!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.03,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你只知道她是个遇上麻烦的小姑娘\NFor all you knew, she was just a little girl in trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.77,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也许她还是你唯一剩下的家人\Nand probably the only family you had left!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不止如此\NIt is more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我相信  这种情况下\NI believe, and what is pissing me off
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,让我生气的是  我不明白为什么\Nabout this situation is I don't understand why --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-你为什么不信  -因为我信不起\N- Why don't you believe? - Because I can't afford to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:26.18,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你可以拥有信念  我得现实一点\NYou get to have faith. I have to be the realist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.74,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我必须得权衡一切  考虑大局\NI'm the one that has to weigh everything and measure everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:32.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,即使我跟你一样为她心碎\NEven in situations where my heart is breaking just as much as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.46,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,有些事谁也说不准\NWe don't know what we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:38.71,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也许亚蕾克西会回来  也许她没有走远\NMaybe Lexi will come back. Maybe she's not too far gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:41.62,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也许  我说不好  也许阴差阳错\NMaybe -- I don't know -- in some unimaginable way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:43.15,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,发生的一切都是必须发生的\Neverything that happened needed to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:45.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好让事情按正确的轨迹发展\Nso that things work out the way they're supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:45.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.78,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你不是说过不能拥有信念吗\NI thought you said you couldn't afford to have faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我没有  我不能  但我有希望\NI don't. I can't. I have hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:56.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这是不同的  信念是你的职责\NThere's a difference. Faith is your department.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:59.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,所以我有你  需要你\NThat's why I have you. That's why I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你说得对\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:07.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们继续恪尽职守吧\NLet's just stick to what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:09.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我来杀迅猎兽  治疗人们\NI'll kill Skitters. I'll patch people up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:12.80,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而你  飞向月球\NYou'll fly to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果我们都活下来了  我们再...\NAnd if we both survive, we'll just --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:21.55,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,去弄明白其余的事\Nwe'll just figure out the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:23.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,成交吗\NDeal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:25.46,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,成交\NDeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:31.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,刚刚可真是剑拔弩张\NQuite the melodrama back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:35.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,怒气冲冲的\NStomping off, all in a huff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:37.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你在冰箱里找东西啊\NYou raiding the, uh, icebox here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:40.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是啊  我找点东西来敷手腕\NYeah, I'm trying to find something for my wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.52,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,疼死了\NIt hurts like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,维柯丁止痛药  你不是不吃了吗\NVicodin. I thought you said you gave this stuff up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-是啊  -怎么  掉了一片指甲\N- I am. - So, what -- you chip a nail,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就旧瘾复发吗  是吗\Nand you've fallen off the wagon again? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,告诉你  你承诺过要保持清醒的\NI'll tell you, you got one hell of a commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:50.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\Nto sobriety, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:53.18,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你现在也许该闭嘴了\NOkay, you might want to shut up right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.69,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也许你应该先考虑清楚\NMaybe you should think twice before you go on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:57.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,再去到处进行演讲  说着以前的莎拉\Ngiving these big public speeches about the old Sarah
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:59.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,和现在的莎拉  还有你戒掉了这东西\Nand the new Sarah and how you're off all this crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,知道吗  我居然真的信了\N'cause you know what? I actually believed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.77,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我真是傻逼啊\NWhat an idiot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我刚想这么说\NTook the words right out of my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:12.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,马特成为了一名真正的战士\NMatt's turned into quite the soldier --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:15.19,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,跋涉几个小时  吃得很少  也不抱怨\NHiking for hours, low rations, no complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:17.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你确定带上他是个好主意吗\NAre you sure it was a good idea to bring him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:20.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,科奇斯说风险很低\NCochise said it was low-risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,肯定比开垦计划要安全\NIt's got to be safer than that reclamation project.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:25.19,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,在那里扭伤的脚踝和伤口\NThere's enough sprained ankles and cuts
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.47,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一辈子都好不完\Nto last a lifetime there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.39,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,什么味道\NWhat's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:34.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我觉得是氯气\NI think it's chlorine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:38.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这片地区有致命的毒气\NThere are lethal patches of toxicity throughout this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,马修  你打开行李袋\NMatthew, if you'll open your duffel bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:41.92,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好\NUh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你们都得戴上\NYou'll all need to put one of these on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:47.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,真好\NOh, lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:59.03,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你究竟为何\NAny particular reason
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:01.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,要在毒废料场藏东西\Nyou decided to hide your stash in a toxic dump?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:05.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,毒气能有效防止食腐动物入侵\NThe toxicity is an effective deterrent to scavengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.11,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们沃尔姆可以呼吸氯气\NWe Volm can breathe chlorine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:11.03,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,补给站在这个水箱下面四英尺的地方\NThe cache is buried 4 feet below this cistern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:13.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你应该有办法进去吧\NI assume you have a way to access it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:15.34,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,马特\NMatt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:17.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,米拉\NMira?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:25.15,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:29.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,坚持住\NHang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:39.74,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她会没事的吧\NShe gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:41.71,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我能呼吸了\NI can breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:44.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你在这里待着  离那边远点就没事\NYou'll be all right over here, away from that crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:46.62,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这里\NWhat are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.11,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我终于出来了\NI finally got out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我做到了  马特  我逃出来了\NI did it, Matt. I escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.77,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,马特跟我们说了你的很多事\NMatt told us a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:53.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,看来你俩在集中营里互相照顾\NSounds like you guys looked out for each other at that camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:54.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,马特救了我的命\NMatt kept me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:57.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我真害怕我永远也逃不出来\NI was afraid I'd never get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:13:58.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你怎么逃出来的\NYeah, how did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.78,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我是照你的吩咐做的\NI did just what you told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:03.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我假装和他们相处融洽  直到他们让我毕业\NI pretended to go along with them until they let me graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样\NWhat was that like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:08.79,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,太古怪了\NOh, man, it was so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.91,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,队长肯特教了我很多\NTeam leader Kent taught me all these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:13.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,比如怎么找难民  逃亡者和军人\Nlike how to find refugees, escapees, militias,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:16.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如何让他们信任你  如何发警报\Nhow to get them to trust you, how to raise the alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.76,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,等等  你说发警报是什么意思\NWait. W-what does that mean, raise the alarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.15,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果我们发现外人  就该吹响\NThere was this whistle that we were supposed to blow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一个口哨\Nif we found any outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:25.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他们特别想让我们找到家庭成员\NThey especially wanted us to track down family members --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,找到相信我们的人\NPeople that would trust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,口哨会叫来激光飞船  进行袭击\NThe whistle calls a beamer strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:30.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,然后迅猎兽会来吗\NAnd then the Skitters come?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:33.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不  青年集中营的队长们会来\NNo, team leaders from the youth camp I was held in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:36.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,抓住这些异议分子  然后带回艾士芬尼\NThey capture the dissidents and take them back to the Espheni.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:37.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你的口哨呢\NWhere's your whistle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.44,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我一出来就把它丢进了河里\NI-I threw it in the river as soon as I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我才不想要那些东西\NI didn't want any part of that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:45.59,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,真高兴你找到了我\NI'm so glad you found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:49.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,真走运\NPretty lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.59,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我躲在树林里\NI was hiding in the woods,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:54.66,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,看着道路  等着会带我和他们一起走的人\Nwatching the road for someone who would take me with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:57.68,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,然后你们来了  我以为我看见了马特\NAnd then you all came along, and I thought I saw Matt,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:15:00.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但我猜那只是我痴心妄想\Nbut I figured it was just wishful thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.78,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,所以你刚好碰到我们吗\NSo, you just happened to come across us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.27,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,在沃尔姆补给站\NAt a Volm weapons cache.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我完全不知道\NYeah, I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:09.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,拜托  你们必须得相信我\NPlease, you have to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:11.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,米拉  这样做是为了大家的安全  站起来\NMira, what I have to do is keep everybody safe. Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,爸爸  你要干什么\NDad, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,爸爸  她是我的朋友\NDad, she's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.62,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道  希望那是真的  马特\NI know. I hope that's true, Matt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但我不会冒险\Nbut I'm not gonna take any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:19.60,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不能把她扔在这里啊\NCan't just leave her here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:20.32,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们不会把她扔在这里\NWe're not gonna leave her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:22.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她要在这里歇着  直到我们完成过来的任务\NShe's gonna rest here while we do what we came to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:41.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这些是管道还是触手\NAre these tubes or tentacles?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:44.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,艾士芬尼科技模仿的是肌肉骨骼系统\NEspheni technology mimics a musculoskeletal system.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:47.89,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,线是连起来的  它们的动作是协调的\NThe cords are connected, and their movement is coordinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:52.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,所以  如果我拉动这根线\NSo, if I pull on... this cord...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,有东西动了  我听到了\NSomething moved. I heard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:01.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,试试另外一根\NTry another.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.52,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是从那边传来的\NThat came from over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.74,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这两条绳子是相连的\NThese two are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:14.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们得进到墙里面\NWe have to get inside these walls
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,标注线之间的联系\Nand map the connections between the cords,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:18.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,得出一个判断结论\NCreate a diagnostic
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:20.66,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,表明哪根线控制什么动作\Nshowing which cords control which movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:23.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,只有挖出激光飞船  我们才能做到\NWhich we can't get to until the beamer has been unearthed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:28.87,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你真的觉得震荡炮\NYou really think those concussion ordnances
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:29.78,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,能完成任务吗\Ncan do the trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:35.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我就当你默认了\NOkay, I'll take that as a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,为什么跟着我\NWhy are you following me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:44.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,因为没人能离开我\NBecause nobody walks away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是吗  以为自己很了不起啊  珀普\NOh, god. Think much of yourself, Pope?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.62,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,关你什么事  你想让我痛苦吗\NWhat do you care?! Do you want me to be in pain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:50.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-是吗  -没错\N- Is that it?! - Right now?! yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.27,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-这里以前是个博物馆  -知道吗\N- Think this used to be a museum. - You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,让我一个人待着\NJust -- just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:54.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,闭嘴啊\NShut up, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:55.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:56.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不是说你\NNo, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:16:59.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我能听见珀普和莎拉的对话\NI can hear Pope and Sarah's conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:00.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,珀普很凶\Nand Pope's being a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.91,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,莎拉的声音好尖\NSarah's voice is a really shrill voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:04.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你会习惯的\NYou'll get used to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你总能听到所有人的对话吗\NDo you listen to everyone's conversations all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:09.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,现在不会  你会慢慢学会怎么无视的\NNo, not anymore. You, um... you learn to tune things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那你就走好了\NYou know what? Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:13.19,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,天哪  我希望这些声音消失\NGod, I want them out of my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.18,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,转移一下注意力  这边\NFocus on something else. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:21.23,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没事  来吧  从这儿跳下去很容易的\NIt's okay. Come on. We could easily make this jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:22.87,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不要  我不想跳\NNo, no, uh, I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.47,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,很简单的  来吧  我教你\NIt's a piece of cake. Come on. I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:27.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,本  你别管我了行吗\NBen, just leave me alone, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.07,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,走开\NBack off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:32.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没事的  我知道感觉会有点怪\NIt's okay. I -- I know it feels weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不是怪  是被侵入的感觉\NNo, it doesn't feel weird. It feels invasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:37.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就好像我身体内有东西在爬  在侵占我\NLike something's crawling inside of me, taking me over,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:39.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但我却毫无办法\Nand there's nothing I can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:40.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,玛吉  我保证  有天\NMaggie, I promise, one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:41.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你会爱上你的新能力\Nyou're gonna love your new powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:44.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你会比以前更强更霸气\NYou're gonna be stronger and more badass than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:47.54,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这话真中听\NThat sounds pretty sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:48.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是啊  你相信我吗\NIt is. Trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:04.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,3  2  1\N3...2...1.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:17.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\NYou okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.72,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我的手好痛\NMy hands are killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不能放开你\NWell, I can't untie you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:24.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我理解\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:29.19,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我好想你\NI missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.29,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我也是\NI missed you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:35.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,真的很痛吗\NDo they really hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我觉得手要被勒断了\NThe rope is cutting into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他绑的太紧了\NHe tied it too tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:44.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道我一定会后悔的\NI know I'm gonna regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:46.23,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,别傻了\NDon't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:54.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谢谢  马特  真的\NThank you, Matt... really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,过来\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:06.77,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,知道吗  你走后我在改教营过的很艰难\NYou know, it was really hard in the camp after you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:10.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我是想让你和我们一起走的  但\NW-well, I wanted to make you come with us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:14.77,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道  但你知道吗\NI know. But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,其实我很高兴我没有那么做\NI'm actually glad I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:21.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我学到了很多\NI learned so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:22.87,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:25.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们把一切都想错了\NWe were wrong about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:31.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你真的应该留下的\NYou really should have stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:34.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不要\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:39.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不  说真的\NNo, seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我从没感觉这么棒过\Nthat's the most amazing I've ever felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:44.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,真不理解你居然不经常跳楼\NI don't know how you're not jumping off of roofs all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,换做是我只要有机会我就会上去\NI'd be up there every chance I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:50.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,其实我刚开始  也像你这样\NWell, uh... I kind of was, in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我会在夜里偷偷跑出去\NI mean, I'd sneak out at night
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:55.71,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,从高处跳下或者奔跑\Nand jump or run faster
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,跑得前所未有的快\Nthan I've ever run before in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:58.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就好像在比赛中一样\Nalmost like I was in a race,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,只是  参赛者只有我一个\NExcept, I guess, it was only a race with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:03.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,后来我发现  我会吓到别人\NEventually, I realized I was freaking people out,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:07.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我就只在必要情况下才显露\Nso I brought it down to a need-to-jump basis, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:10.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我想我会经常跳的\NI think I'm gonna need to jump a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:11.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们可以一起跳\NWe can jump together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,只要提前给大家说一声\NWe'll just warn everybody first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:15.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就这么定了\NDeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:18.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样\NHow are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:22.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,感觉很棒  太赞了\NLike, great, amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我是说移植后的疼痛\NI mean, your pain from the transplant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:25.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,还感觉的到吗\NIs it still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没有  不痛了\NNo. It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:34.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我突然发现的\NI'm just realizing it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,刺钉逐渐感觉到它们\NThe spikes are starting to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:38.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是你的一部分了\Nthat they're part of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:43.23,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,等等  你说的好像它们自己有思想一样\NWait. You make it seem like they've got a mind of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:43.92,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,它们有的\NThey do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:47.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,它不仅是肉体的力量\NThis isn't just physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:50.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是种外星生物在试图融入你的人类基因\NThere's an alien life-form fusing with your human DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:53.11,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,它是  想要控制你的\NIt -- it wants to control all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:54.74,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,它想\NIt wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:57.89,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是的  它有感觉  有愿望\NYes, it has feelings, desires
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:01.52,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,比你经历过的都要强得多\Nstronger than anything you've ever felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:04.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,所以  我可能会非常非常生气\NSo, I'm gonna be really, really mad sometimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,或者非常非常饿\NAnd really, really hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:07.89,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,天哪\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:10.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而且会好奇  害怕\NAnd curious and afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:13.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,或者  有时候\Nand... sometimes really, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:17.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,深深坠入爱河\Nin love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:21.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,当你快乐时  你会处于狂喜之中\NAnd... when you're happy, you're ecstatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:25.32,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,有时候我会想起入侵之前的生活\NSometimes I think about life before the invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:30.32,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们在波士顿  坐在我屋里  看着书\NWe were back in Boston, sitting in my room, reading a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:34.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我觉得好快乐  都没法收起脸上的笑容\NAnd I feel so happy, I can't stop smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:36.55,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但接着\NBut then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:42.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,怎么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:46.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我会想起我妈妈  想起我失去了她\NI think about my mom -- losing my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:52.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,积极和消极的感受都会被放大\NIt works both ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:06.46,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我能感到你的悲伤  好像是自己的一样\NI can feel your sadness like... like it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:07.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这倒是第一次见\NThat's new.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:13.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我想我们只能习惯这点了\NI guess we're just gonna have to get used to that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:16.19,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,从现在开始  你要多加小心\NYou have to be careful, from now on, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:19.79,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,在你学会掌控你的力量前\Nit's easy to get overwhelmed and lose yourself until...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:21.92,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你会很容易崩溃  会迷失自我\Nyou learn to control your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:24.71,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:26.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我要怎么做\NHow do I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:29.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,多用用它\NUse it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:31.43,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,准备好找点乐子了吗\NReady to have some fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:38.80,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-漂亮  -武器\N- Good! - Weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.93,0:22:40.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们可以带走\NWe'll take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:43.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,真棒\NOutstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:44.88,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,要小心这个\NNow, be very careful with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:46.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这是什么\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:48.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,次空间通讯器\NSubspace communicator.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:51.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,精确调整过  可以接收所有艾士芬尼的通讯\NHighly tuned to all manner of Espheni communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:54.39,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,它可以帮助我们穿过敌人的防火墙\NThis will enhance our ability to cut through enemy firewalls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:22:57.32,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,和数光年外的沃尔姆援军的联络\Nto contact Volm reinforcements light-years away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:22:58.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,弄坏了你要赔哦\NYou break it, you buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:00.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那震荡炮呢\NWhat about the compression ordnance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.05,0:23:02.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那不是我们来的目的吗\NWasn't that the main reason for our joyride here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:03.74,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,爸  爸\NDad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.10,0:23:06.29,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不是说让你别去接近她吗\NI thought I told you to leave her back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:10.03,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不该放开她的  但她说手很痛\NI shouldn't have untied her! But her hands hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:12.32,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她把这个藏在了鞋子里  而且吹响了\NShe had this in her shoe, and she blew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:14.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你有什么要解释的吗\NYou want to explain yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.69,0:23:20.30,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不  我宽恕你  汤姆·梅森\NNo. Let me forgive you, Tom Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:22.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,天哪  她是他们的人了\NOh, god, she's on their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:26.51,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们得撤离这里\NWe need to get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:28.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,大家找掩护  这边\NEverybody take cover! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:30.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,米拉  米拉\NMira! Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:34.29,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我还没找到震荡炮呢\NI haven't located the concussion ordnance yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:35.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,快走\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:55.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,有什么要和我说的吗\NYou got something to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.53,0:23:58.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没什么\NNot particularly, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:24:01.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没有  真的吗  一句也没有吗\NNo? Really, not -- not a word to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:02.69,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你真打算站在这儿\NAre you honestly gonna stand there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.69,0:24:04.26,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,跟我因为我没说的话辩论吗\Ndebating me on what I haven't even said yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.41,0:24:06.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,难以置信\NUnbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.58,0:24:07.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你知道什么才是难以置信吗\NNo, you know what's unbelievable?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.59,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是你根本不用去想\NWhat's unbelievable is that you never have to wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.61,0:24:10.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一个人究竟是什么样\Nwhat a person's really like --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.12,0:24:12.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我是说他的内在\NI mean really like, on the inside --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.81,0:24:14.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,因为你和一个人接触的越多\N'cause the more you hang out with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.08,0:24:16.27,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就会越了解他  而他表现出的\Nthe more you get to know them, when they reveal themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.32,0:24:18.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也更贴近真实的自己\Nthey'll show you exactly who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:19.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,让让行吗\NDo you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:23.74,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我已经理解了你伟大的自我展现\NJust so I understand this thunderous revelation of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:27.19,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你觉得我跟你说我是什么样的人了\Nwhat exactly do you think that I told you I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.98,0:24:30.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你是个瘾君子\NYou're an addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.71,0:24:35.23,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,说明你很懦弱  而且是个骗子\NThat means you're weak... and you're a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.62,0:24:37.11,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我没资格评论你\NNow, I'm not the one to judge,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.15,0:24:39.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但你也不是我认识的第一个瘾君子了\Nbut... this isn't my first rodeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.89,0:24:42.34,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我了解你们  而且我不打算成为那个\NI know addicts, and I am not gonna be the one
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.95,0:24:46.18,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,被你利用  被你欺骗\Nthat you use and you lie to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.01,0:24:49.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,然后被你抛弃的人\Nand then move along.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.61,0:24:51.80,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,所以  再见吧\NSo bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.85,0:24:55.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我怎么利用你了\NIn what way did I use you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.95,0:24:59.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,告诉我啊  我怎么利用你了\NTell me! In what way did I use you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.85,0:25:02.98,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,遇见你之前我过的很好\NI was fine before I met you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.19,0:25:04.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,从来没有被迅猎兽袭击过\NI-I'd never been attacked by skitters!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.91,0:25:06.59,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也没有杀过任何东西\NI had never killed anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.75,0:25:08.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但我一直和你并肩作战\NBut I fought with you, side by side,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.53,0:25:10.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,为了你冒着生命危险\Nrisking my life for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.50,0:25:12.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你就看见我手里拿了一瓶药\NAnd you see me with one pill bottle in my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.66,0:25:15.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你就认定我是骗子和瘾君子吗\Nand your go-to response is that I am a liar and a user?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.80,0:25:19.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你知道我怎么想吗  我想是你胆怯了\NYou know what I think? I think you're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.20,0:25:23.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你害怕我们可能的将来\NI think you're afraid of what we might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.15,0:25:27.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,别给我费劲分析了  我没兴趣\NSpare me the analysis. I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.25,0:25:29.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,显而易见\NObviously not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.04,0:25:32.88,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你知道这瓶里是什么吗\NYou know what's in this bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.30,0:25:34.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,维柯丁[止痛药]\NVicodin!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.99,0:25:35.98,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,阿司匹林\NAspirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.21,0:25:39.76,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一切都乱套的时候标签弄错了\NThe labels got mixed up when everything went to crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.04,0:25:44.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,用心看里面  才知道装的是什么\NYou do actually have to look to know what's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.56,0:25:53.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,马特  马特\NMatt! Matt!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.11,0:25:56.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-你见到马特了吗  -我想他去那边了\N- Have you seen Matt? - I think he went that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.50,0:26:00.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是青年营的领队\NIt's the team leaders from the youth camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.22,0:26:14.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,冲啊  乔尔  冲啊\NGo, Joe, go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.05,0:26:37.89,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,米拉  救救我\NMira... help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.96,0:26:39.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,太晚了\NIt's too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.32,0:26:58.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他跑不了了  抓住他\NThis one isn't going anywhere. Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.08,0:27:05.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,米拉  救救我\NMira, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.20,0:27:14.76,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,科奇斯\NCochise!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.64,0:27:24.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这个眩晕弹应该能拖住他们几小时\NThat stun should hold them for a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.05,0:27:27.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,带着这个什么也看不见\NI can't see in this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.09,0:27:31.30,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这里的空气没问题  你可以摘下面罩了\NThe air's okay here! You can take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.87,0:27:35.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我没子弹了  你还好吗\NI'm empty. You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.14,0:27:36.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我也没了  我还好\NI got nothing left. Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.87,0:27:50.44,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们得找个更好的掩护\NWe need to find better cover than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.42,0:27:59.44,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,安\NAnne!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.27,0:28:03.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\NYou all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.34,0:28:05.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没事\NI'm okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.40,0:28:07.89,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,待在原地不要动\NStay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.86,0:28:12.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,汤姆·梅森  我是肯特·马修领队\NTom Mason, this is team leader Kent Matthew.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.65,0:28:15.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们抓住了你儿子  马特\NWe have your son, Matt!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.02,0:28:17.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他晕了过去\NHe is subdued!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.57,0:28:19.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,现在给他打了镇定剂\NHe's being collected right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.30,0:28:32.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们不想伤害你  汤姆\NWe don't want to hurt you, Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.22,0:28:34.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们是来带你去安全的地方的\NWe're here to take you to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.12,0:28:36.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,战争结束了\NThe war is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.72,0:28:38.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们的艾士芬尼兄弟姐妹想要\NOur Espheni brothers want to
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.08,0:28:40.15,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,欢迎我们进入他们的社会\Nwelcome us into their society!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.01,0:28:43.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,请你和我们走吧  汤姆\NPlease, come with us, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.86,0:28:59.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你没子弹了  汤姆\NYou're out of bullets, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.81,0:29:07.72,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,现在只是时间问题了\NNow it's just a matter of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.75,0:29:09.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,出来吧  我不会伤害你\NCome out! I won't attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.11,0:29:11.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,停战\NTruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.06,0:29:14.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那些烟可是有毒的  汤姆\NThose fumes are toxic, Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.87,0:29:16.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那个集装箱随时都可能爆炸\NThat container could explode at any moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.10,0:29:18.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你最好还是出来吧\NYou better come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.62,0:29:31.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,等一下\NHey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.01,0:29:33.78,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,安\NAnne?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.86,0:29:34.88,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,等一下\NHey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.49,0:30:08.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你怎么能对自己人做出这种事情\NHow could you do this to your own people?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.70,0:30:13.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,只有接受艾士芬尼兄弟们我们才能进步\NProgress is made when we embrace our Espheni brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.54,0:30:19.91,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不是叛徒  我是新的爱国者\NI'm not a traitor. I'm a new patriot.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.50,0:30:30.30,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,汤姆\NTom...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.25,0:30:34.77,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我把我母亲  交给了它们\NI gave them...my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.95,0:30:55.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,快到了  就快到了\NHere you are. Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.81,0:30:59.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他在这\NHere he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.99,0:31:01.72,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,老爸\NDad.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.88,0:31:14.39,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你决定留下了吗\NYou decided to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.82,0:31:16.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.02,0:31:19.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我以为你跟莎拉一起走了\NI figured you were going with Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.89,0:31:21.68,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她几个小时前来过\NShe came by a few hours ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.28,0:31:24.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,拿走了一把步枪和几天的口粮\NPicked up a rifle, a couple days' rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.34,0:31:25.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,怎么会呢\NHow?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.89,0:31:28.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她说她知道附近有座农场\NShe said she knew of a nearby farm
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.09,0:31:29.30,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那里可能会有些食物\Nwhere there might be some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.10,0:31:31.71,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我以为你会跟她一起去呢\NI just assumed you were going with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.25,0:31:40.55,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好了  展示一下你的本领吧\NOkay, let's see what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.17,0:31:47.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,正中目标\NBull's-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.07,0:32:01.60,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,继续  那边还有很多\NKeep going. Plenty more where that came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.37,0:32:23.72,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你现在觉得我怎么样\NHow do you like me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.17,0:32:32.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我太喜欢你了\NI like you too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.04,0:33:05.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.68,0:33:06.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不应该那么做\NI shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.12,0:33:08.43,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你做了  不过...\NI'm glad you did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.28,0:33:11.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-哈尔  -是的\N- Hal. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.17,0:33:15.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,天哪  我疯了吗  我...\NOh, my God, am I going crazy? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.14,0:33:18.71,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,自从我醒来之后有了刺钉\NSince I woke up with the spikes,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.72,0:33:21.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我就感觉  被你吸引住了\NI feel like... I'm drawn to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.24,0:33:23.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你以前没有这种感觉吗\NYeah, and you didn't before?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.67,0:33:26.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没有  我爱  我爱哈尔\NNo, I love -- I love hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.41,0:33:30.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这个  这种感觉不一样\NThis... this feels different.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.45,0:33:31.88,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,天哪  这种感觉太强烈了\NGod, this is so intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.59,0:33:33.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我...\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.93,0:33:38.77,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我现在太想吻你了\NI really want to kiss you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.12,0:33:41.80,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不要\NDon't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.42,0:33:44.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道\NI know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.45,0:33:47.62,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.15,0:33:51.03,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,天哪\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.68,0:33:55.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,看来我们暂时  不会遇到阻碍了\NLooks like we're in the clear... for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.53,0:33:58.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我应该向大家道歉\NI owe you all an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.50,0:34:01.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我误导了你们  给你们带来了不必要的危险\NI misled you, put you at unnecessary risk,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.87,0:34:04.47,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而且我们甚至没有拿到我们要找的东西\Nand we did not even retrieve the essential item we came for.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.34,0:34:07.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们回去之后\NWe'll just have to dig a little harder
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.08,0:34:08.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,努力点把飞船挖出来就是了  科奇斯\Nwhen we get back, Cochise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.52,0:34:11.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你怎么样\NHow are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.39,0:34:13.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,很疼\NIt hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.78,0:34:15.51,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就像一千多根针在扎我\Nlike a thousand needles sticking into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.57,0:34:16.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我想也是\NBet it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.61,0:34:21.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我在米拉的事上犯傻了\NSorry about being such an idiot about Mira.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.70,0:34:22.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你才13岁\NYou're 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.80,0:34:23.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,早恋也不容易\Npuppy love is not easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.05,0:34:25.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,特别是在生死攸关的时候\Nespecially when it's life-and-death.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.08,0:34:27.30,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这不是早恋  老爸\NIt's not puppy love, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.70,0:34:32.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我想让你忘了她  但我觉得你未必能做到\NI'd tell you to forget about her, but I doubt you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.17,0:34:36.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,听上去可能有些奇怪\NStrange as it sounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.22,0:34:38.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但那应该记住你对她的感觉\Nyou should try to remember the feeling you had for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.26,0:34:39.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这种感觉很重要\NThe feeling is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.78,0:34:40.60,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.39,0:34:47.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,因为你在生活中  很难遇到一个\N'Cause it's pretty rare in life when you meet somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.65,0:34:50.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,彼此都很在意对方的人\Nwho cares about you as much as you do about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.45,0:34:59.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,玛吉怎么样了\NHey, how did things go with Maggie?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.84,0:35:01.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,还行  挺好\NFine. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.06,0:35:06.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你的那些  刺钉\NThose-- those spikes of yours --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.01,0:35:08.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,它们能帮你很快愈合  对吧\Nthey help you heal quickly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.81,0:35:10.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-是的  -很好\N- Yeah. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.75,0:35:16.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你应该帮玛吉适应她的刺钉\NYou were supposed to help Maggie adjust to her spikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.86,0:35:19.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,并不意味着可以对我女朋友有想法\Ndoesn't mean it's open season on my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.47,0:35:21.18,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-哈尔  我绝不会  -本\N- Hal, I would never -- - You know what, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.20,0:35:22.92,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,省省吧  我都看见了\NJust save it, okay? Because I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.44,0:35:24.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我明白\NAnd, look, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.18,0:35:26.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她很漂亮  很出众  但她是我的人\NShe's gorgeous. She's amazing. But she's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.06,0:35:28.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不好意思\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.51,0:35:31.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我没看见她脖子上有你的链子\NI didn't see your leash on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.17,0:35:38.51,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,离她远点\NJust stay away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.59,0:35:49.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,大家好\NHey, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.07,0:35:52.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我还有点担心你们呢\NI was starting to worry about you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.90,0:35:55.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们遇到了点麻烦  不过有惊无险\NWe ran into a little trouble. We made it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.40,0:35:56.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,老爸\NDad!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.69,0:35:58.78,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一切都顺利吗\NEverything go okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.06,0:36:03.29,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你的脸怎么了\NWhat happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.88,0:36:04.98,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没事\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.60,0:36:08.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.34,0:36:10.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,丁甘\NDingaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.44,0:36:12.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那个外星引擎修得怎么样了\NHow goes the alien small-engine repair?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.54,0:36:13.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不怎么样\NNot great.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.89,0:36:16.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这些碎石使得我们无法靠近控制设施\NThe rubble prevents us getting to the necessary controls.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.09,0:36:18.69,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你们找没找到那个\NWere you able to bring back that tool
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.71,0:36:19.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,挖掘激光飞船的工具\Nto help us raise the Beamer?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.70,0:36:20.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没有  我们遇到了埋伏\NNo, we got ambushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.98,0:36:22.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那个补给站被摧毁了\NThe cache was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.80,0:36:25.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,又回到了原点  不过这也不是第一次了\NBack to square one, but it wouldn't be the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.20,0:36:26.34,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,睡觉前把这些武器\NLet's get these weapons and supplies
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.36,0:36:27.98,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,和物资收拾起来\Nstowed before we get some shut-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.92,0:36:34.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我找到了这个\NI did find this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.57,0:36:36.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,按理说  这个可以召唤激光飞船\NSupposedly, this can call Beamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.41,0:36:38.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不知道是靠特定的音色还是频率\NI don't know if it's a tone or a frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.31,0:36:40.11,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你看看能研究出什么来  小心一点\NSee what you can do with it. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.64,0:36:41.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,千万别吹\NDo not blow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.97,0:36:43.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我去找沙研究一下  你来吗\NI'll take it to Shaq right away. Coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.81,0:36:44.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.74,0:36:47.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,现在\NNow...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.35,0:36:52.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你们两个小子有什么要跟我说的吗\Nanything you boys need to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.64,0:36:55.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.05,0:37:03.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.81,0:37:12.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你听听我记的对不对\NSo, let me see if I remember this correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.52,0:37:14.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们被包围了\NWe were surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.86,0:37:18.11,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,情况很糟糕  只有一个办法能出去\NSituation sucked, and only one way out,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.13,0:37:20.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,有一个人需要牺牲自己  我\NAnd that's for one of us to be dead -- me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.23,0:37:23.03,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,有一个人需要聪明的活下去  你\NOne has to be smart and stay alive -- you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.06,0:37:26.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这是我们交战时的基本准则\NThose are the basic rules of engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.30,0:37:29.72,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我在"山区碉堡社区大学"里教过这一课\NUsed to teach a course on it at Bunker Hill Community College.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.75,0:37:30.87,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,饶了我吧\NGive me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.95,0:37:33.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,可是你没做出聪明人该做的事\NBut instead of doing the smart thing, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.86,0:37:37.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果我没记错的话  你手无寸铁地跑了出去\Nif my memory serves, ran out without a weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.32,0:37:39.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没有任何计划  还大喊了一句\Nwithout a plan, and yelled --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.41,0:37:41.07,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,什么来着  "等一下"\Nwhat was it, again? -- "Hey, wait"?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.44,0:37:42.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我当时不知道该说什么\NI didn't know what else to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.85,0:37:45.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,"等一下"就是你的神勇计划\N"Hey, wait"? that was your big master kamikaze plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.15,0:37:47.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,"等一下  看那里\N"Hey, wait, look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.14,0:37:48.66,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,等一下  别杀他  杀我"\NHey, wait, don't shoot him! Shoot me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.15,0:37:50.68,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你以为你要死了\NI thought you were going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.33,0:37:54.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.56,0:37:58.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果你中枪的话  我可能也会做\NI probably would have done the same dumbass thing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.45,0:38:00.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这种蠢事\Nif you were the one getting shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.99,0:38:03.46,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但是我在想\NBut I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.10,0:38:07.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,子弹没打中你可能是有原因的\NMaybe there's a reason the bullets missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.50,0:38:10.18,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你说"如果我们这次能活下去\NWhen you said to me, "If we survive this,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.19,0:38:11.15,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们会解决好其它事的"\Nwe'll figure out the rest,"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.18,0:38:12.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这让我听了很难受\NThat was very hard for me to hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.27,0:38:13.92,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,因为我不知道"其它事"是指什么\Nbecause I don't really know what "the rest" means,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.94,0:38:17.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但是  我后来意识到我才不关心呢\Nbut... then I realized I don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.59,0:38:23.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,无论这段时间是长是短\NWhether it's a long time or a short time,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.47,0:38:26.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我都想跟你在一起\NI just want to spend it with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.13,0:38:29.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意的话\Nif you'll have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.36,0:38:32.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-这听上去好像是...  -就是\N- That sounds like... - It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.37,0:38:39.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,天哪\NMy God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.68,0:38:41.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道这不容易\NI'm not saying it's gonna be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.22,0:38:44.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但你愿意嫁给我吗\NBut will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.60,0:38:48.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,愿意\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.58,0:38:51.71,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,等一下  我们怎么知道这么做是不是对的\NWait. How do we know we're doing the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.74,0:38:52.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不知道  我们不知道\NWe don't. We don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.90,0:38:57.11,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但我还抱有希望\NBut I have hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.51,0:38:59.26,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,愿意\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.41,0:39:01.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我愿意\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.68,0:39:24.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我承诺在交战时永远支持你\NI promise to always have your back in a firefight,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.13,0:39:25.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我也承诺尽量不被杀死\Nand I promise to try not to get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.29,0:39:27.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我的承诺与你一样\NI promise to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.39,0:39:34.27,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,安  你是否愿意与他一起\NSo, Anne... do you take this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.18,0:39:38.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,无论情况好坏\Nfor better, for worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.62,0:39:41.62,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,富贵贫贱\Nfor richer, for poorer...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.40,0:39:45.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,疾病健康\Nin sickness or in health...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.74,0:39:48.19,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,直到死亡将你们分开\Ntill death do you part?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.08,0:39:51.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是的  我愿意\NYeah. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.52,0:39:54.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我也愿意\NI do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.73,0:39:59.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,据我所知  你现在可以亲吻新娘了\NWell, as far as I'm concerned, you may kiss the bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.11,0:40:07.43,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,汤姆·梅森  我必须要跟你谈谈\NTom Mason... I must speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.62,0:40:09.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上  我们在举行婚礼啊\NFor God's sake, we're having a wedding here!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.45,0:40:11.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,等我跟汤姆·梅森谈完\NYou may resume your ritual
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.98,0:40:13.78,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,激光飞船的事  你们的仪式可以继续进行\Nafter I speak to Tom Mason about the Beamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.30,0:40:17.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,激光飞船更重要\NThe Beamer is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.17,0:40:21.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,恭喜你们\NCongratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.38,0:40:27.26,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你为什么要打断我们\NSo, why the hell did you interrupt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.01,0:40:31.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我一直在分解你带回来的艾士芬尼的哨子\NI have been deconstructing the Espheni whistle you brought back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.78,0:40:32.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你说对了\NYou are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.26,0:40:34.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,它可以跟激光飞船直接通信\NIt communicates directly with the Beamer...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.53,0:40:37.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,发动引擎\Nengaging the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.49,0:40:38.77,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好吧  它还能干什么\NOkay, what else can it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.64,0:40:42.43,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,它能得到月球的归航信标吗\NCan it access the homing beacon on the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.90,0:40:46.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,需要一个不同的信号\NA different signal is required
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.61,0:40:49.55,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,来指引激光飞船飞向某个特定地方  不过\Nto direct the Beamer to a certain location... but --
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.59,0:40:52.34,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不过这是个开始\NBut he's saying it's one hell of a start,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.37,0:40:54.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你这个疯子\NYou crazy son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.54,0:40:58.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我分离出了哨子的归航振幅\NI was able to isolate the homing amplitude of the whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.29,0:41:01.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是超声频率  人类听不到\NIt is an ultrasonic frequency that humans can't hear
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.04,0:41:04.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而且人类的技术也不知道该找什么\Nand human tech wouldn't know to look for.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.78,0:41:07.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我用这个通信器捕捉到了这个信号\NI've captured the signal within this communicator.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.17,0:41:09.74,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好的  这对我们有什么帮助\NOkay. How does it help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.20,0:41:21.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,退后\NStand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.85,0:41:22.55,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,退后\NBack!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.58,0:41:53.91,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我想这就是答案\NI guess that's how.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.06,0:41:57.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们要去月球了\NWe choose to go to the moon.
